What is a directory, and what is its relationship to files? It is my understanding that a directory is still a file but it is the main folder that holds the other files.
How are VCS useful? They allow you to see the edit history of a file so you can go back and see what you have done to it. It allows you to to revert your code back to the previous version if needed.
Do you have a favorite artistic medium? Why is it your favorite? My favorite artistic medium is leather. It is my favorite because it can be very forgiving if you make a mistake. You can also create so many things out of it.
